The terrace & pool on the roof was beautifull, a relaxing place to sit in the sun with nice cocktails.	I would reccomend this hotel to families that need to travel by train in Barcelona and people who want to enjoy a relaxing and luxury holiday.	Modern decor, comfortable bed, a nice relaxing chair, desk etc.	The pool area is great for relaxing after you've done the sights or for a pre dinner drink before you head off to the many nice bars and restaurants in the area.	It's a really good value, very modern hotel in a peaceful neighborhood.